Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw Akai Shuuichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, not too long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a robbery at Teito Bank in Beika City.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said on the news that the trial for the case started yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the video of the incident that they played back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the customers that was freed looked just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I suppose it was just a look-alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, we witnessed it with our own eyes, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When that Akai came to Raiha Pass unsuspectingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And got a bullet in the head, courtesy of Kir's gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call Kir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First it was the Haido City Hotel where\Nthat escapee Sherry showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the place where Akai lured us to in order to snipe us...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was at the Mouri Detective Agency in Beika City.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI also kept Kir in custody at Haido Central Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, a man resembling Akai\Nhas appeared at a bank in Beika City.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haido and Beika are but a stone's throw from one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think that's a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HA22628&}Flowers dance to the piano's rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HA22628&}Two people face-to-face is a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HA22628&}Bomb threats at the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HA22628&}What is the aim of the men in black?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\bord0.1}Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\bord0.1}The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)\bord0.1}His name is: Detective {\t(1450,1451,\1c&H4331B1&)}Conan{\1c&H6AE8FA&}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After school, we came across an old man named Daita Kyouzou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We then detected his intention of committing suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And succeeded in talking some sense into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, at that point, Genta and the others\Nshared with me a surprising revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Among the customers who had become hostages\Nin the bank robbery we'd encountered...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was a man who had also found himself\Ninvolved in the bus-jacking from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, a strange request arrived at the Mouri Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Someone wishes for you to solve the mystery of\Nthe red T-shirts that have been sent every week...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"So please offer your expertise," it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next day, we arrived at Beika\NDepartment Store to meet said person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also there was Agent Jodie from the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person she was looking for was indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already past 1:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The client isn't coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not having it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this paper bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody lose it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be best if you didn't touch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has a bomb inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bomb!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you know something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strapped up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bombs!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't finished our lunch yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much longer is this lunch going to take?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A few things came up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we're still at the department store cafe downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Things"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you encounter problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, once Camel's finished in the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll meet you there, after I finish my iced tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems as if Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ged...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially since that bank robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She told me not to tell James{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth is with the black cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a man with a burnt face who couldn't talk came to buy something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the clerks should be able to remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be he wasn't there in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, who was the man I saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you Shuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Shuu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say that you're Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The edge of the coaster is folded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it like that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Run! This place is dangerous!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You... why do you have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was knocked unconscious from behind in the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I came to, a masked man had put this on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That he'd also put the paper bags in\Nfront of the escalators and stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He threated to blow everything up if I didn't do as he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm calling the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that he'd press the detonator the moment\Nany police approach this department store!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also said if anyone escaped from this floor, it'd be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what does that man want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside this bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that the sender of these 13 red T-shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be located at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red T-shirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the sender...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that they're definitely on this floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're definitely on this floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:19.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't locate the sender of the red T-shirts in that bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll detonate the bombs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The masked man that strapped this bomb to me said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he mentioned that the sender is on this floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said if that person owned up, he wouldn't press the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you hear that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care why you did it, but whoever sent all these red T-shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're here, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one's coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He demanded that the escalators be stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to not let the elevators stop on this floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until the sender is identified...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's locking up all the customers on this floor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,NOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay on this floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fscy120\fscx120}CALM DOWN!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just heard, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomber is searching for whoever\Nkeeps sending him those red T-shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he believes that the sender is on this floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until we locate the sender...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anyone tries to escape this floor, he'll engage the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it'd be over if we informed the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any arbitrary step by one of us will result in casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:13:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but can you call and relay\Nthe situation to the store manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And have them stop the escalator and not\Nallow the elevator to stop on this floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, any use of the stairs will also be disallowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please make absolutely sure that\Nthe police are not informed of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomber could be on this floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watching our every move at this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, what should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about we have a look at those?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The red T-shirts he keeps receiving\Nevery week from the mysterious sender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I say that he had been receiving those weekly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were asked to come here by someone\Nseemingly related to the bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They claimed someone related to the mystery of\Nthe red T-shirts that had been sent weekly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would come to the sports equipment counter\Nin Beika Department Store this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they wanted me, Mouri Kogorou, to take on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogorou?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that great detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here to expose the identities of the\Nred T-shirts' sender and the bomber in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just watch me from a distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man with a burn mark on his right cheek left this shop a bit ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was soon after you left your seat in\Norder to answer your phone outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was he...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wearing a cap like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We crossed paths in the restroom just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man with a burn that looked just like Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I lost sight of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person you said you saw during that bank robbery incident was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He disappeared in the confusion following\Nthat incident, so I started to look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the mark on the back of the cap he was wearing at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found out it was an original design of this department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I came to search for clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was half in doubt so I didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since it looked like he lost his memory and the ability to speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't confirm anything from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think this could be a trap set by them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Akai Shuuichi is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also confirmed the fingerprints on his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both your and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s prints are there, just as you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We also found the fingerprints of the man\Nwhose burnt corpse was found a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know Shuu could've managed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this trap for anyway!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They may try to confuse us and pull something off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The SWAT team?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, something happened on the next floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People were shouting that the elevator wouldn't stop on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the man with the burn must be Shuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a message left to me by that man with a burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:17:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sensed that something would\Nhappen at this department store?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt he must've regained his memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the torn delivery slips\Ninside the bags containing the T-shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seven, six, and five weeks ago,\Ntwo T-shirts were sent per week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But on the fourth week, for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only one was sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, three, two, and one week ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two T-shirts were sent each time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does this mean something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can only say that it totals 13, an unlucky number...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got bombs on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the shoulder of your coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something red on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's red, could that be related to this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is probably just someone's lipstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was on a very crowded bullet train before I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, stay away from me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside the bag that had the T-shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a receipt from when they bought the T-shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The amount matches too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A receipt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the bag that had one T-shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a receipt for one T-shirt as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other bags have them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dates on the receipts match those on the delivery slips.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sent those the same day they bought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the receipts are also torn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't tell where these were bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something can be seen only on last week's receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, they didn't tear it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can see a mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Beika Department Store's mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the time of purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's interesting that all of them were at 12:28.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the bomber knew that the sender would be on this floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He realized the sender always bought them in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be in the sports department?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because the T-shirts are classified as underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It says "underwear" on the receipts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, you'd wear them when you go jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're made out of polyester that absorb sweat and dry easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know where these would be sold?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the fitness supplies section.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Up until two weeks ago, the receipts were torn\Nso that no one could tell the place of purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did they miss only this week's?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think this receipt is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:20:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're trying to hide where it was bought...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You only have to tear the upper left side...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they tore the upper right side too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're just careless?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way they folded the clothes were careless too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way they folded?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, take this single shirt that was sent as example.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are strange creases on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we fold along the creases...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It ends up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we charge in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomber claimed that if we police\Nclose in, he'll send the place up in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the informant, the bombs are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.53,0:21:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't rely on that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They may have said that just because they want to be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to wait here for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And see what the bomber's next move is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long I gotta wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a ghost that may not even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.42,0:22:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be patient, Chianti.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're certain the man that looks like\NAkai entered that department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll decide whether he's a ghost or not with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it turns out that he isn't a ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that exact moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll turn you into a ghost myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,TRANS... {\alpha&HFF&\t(1990,2391,\alpha&H00&)}FORM!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.87,0:24:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so overjoyed I can't contain it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because then, I could kill him all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.79,0:24:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't allow the bombs to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.54,0:24:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the name of the great detective, Mouri Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.04,0:24:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.28,0:24:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.21,0:24:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look Forward to the Next Episode
